#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn43.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn43.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 43 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 43 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 1. Paṭhamavagga → asaṅkhatavaggo (bj)
msgctxt "sn43.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 1. Kāyagatāsatisutta → kāya (pts1)
msgctxt "sn43.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Kāyagatāsatisutta "
msgstr "1. Mindfulness of the Body "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn43.1:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.1:1.2"
msgid "“Asaṅkhatañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi asaṅkhatagāmiñca maggaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you the unconditioned and the path that leads to the unconditioned. "

msgctxt "sn43.1:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha. "
msgstr "Listen … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.1:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhataṃ? "
msgstr "And what is the unconditioned? "

msgctxt "sn43.1:1.5"
msgid "Yo, bhikkhave, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn43.1:1.6"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhataṃ. "
msgstr "This is called the unconditioned. "

msgctxt "sn43.1:1.7"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr "And what is the path that leads to the unconditioned? "

msgctxt "sn43.1:1.8"
msgid "Kāyagatāsati. "
msgstr "Mindfulness of the body. "

msgctxt "sn43.1:1.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo. "
msgstr "This is called the path that leads to the unconditioned. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn43.1:2.1"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṃ vo mayā asaṅkhataṃ, desito asaṅkhatagāmimaggo. "
msgstr "So, mendicants, I’ve taught you the unconditioned and the path that leads to the unconditioned. "

msgctxt "sn43.1:2.2"
msgid "Yaṃ, bhikkhave, satthārā karaṇīyaṃ sāvakānaṃ hitesinā anukampakena anukampaṃ upādāya, kataṃ vo taṃ mayā. "
msgstr "Out of compassion, I’ve done what a teacher should do who wants what’s best for their disciples. "

#. VAR: Jhāyatha → nijjhāyatha (mr)
msgctxt "sn43.1:2.3"
msgid "Etāni, bhikkhave, rukkhamūlāni, etāni suññāgārāni. Jhāyatha, bhikkhave, mā pamādattha; mā pacchā vippaṭisārino ahuvattha. Ayaṃ vo amhākaṃ anusāsanī”ti. "
msgstr "Here are these roots of trees, and here are these empty huts. Practice absorption, mendicants! Don’t be negligent! Don’t regret it later! This is my instruction to you.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn43.1:2.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
